The Emir of Jere in Kagarko local government area of  Kaduna state, Dr. Sa’ad Usman is dead.  The deceased until his death was the husband of Senator Esther Nenadi Usman who represented Kaduna south of Kaduna State and also served as the Minister of Finance during the President Olusegun Obasanjo’s administration .  A younger brother to the late Emir, Aminu Jere disclosed the death of his brother.  According to Aminu, ” Inna Lillahi Wa Inna Illaihi Rajiun, I just lost a brother in person of HRH the Sarkin Jere, Dr Saad Usman, PhD. Janazah at Jere, by 2pm today (Wednesday) Insha Allah” he further said.  Late Dr. Saad Usman was at various times Secretary of the Kaduna State Government.  It would be recalled that the late Chief
was sometimes in 2014 attacked following a land dispute and it was rumoured then that he was dead until the police debunked the rumour.  He was however said to have been flown outside the country for medical attention as a result of injuries sustained during the attack and ever since then, his health status has never been the same until his death.